name: All Monsters Are Human
description:
This is a digital print of my original illustration 'All Monsters Are Human' onto quality SoftStyle T-shirt.

Each one is packaged separately and delivered in a protective plastic postage bag. These shirts are made to order, so please allow up to 2 weeks for your purchase to be mailed out to you.

If you have any questions about these shirts, please do not hesitate to contact me.

All tees are unisex and are available in S, M, L and XL.
